cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with the detection and tracking of sperm in microscopy images using deep learning and modified algorithms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of deep learning networks also suggests the possibility of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) being a relevant category. Finally, the paper deals with microscopy images, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
